Harmony Gold Sees “Modest” Improvement in Hidden Valley Output for Quarter

-- B y   A g n e s   N i k o i
-- 
2011-03-29T06:52:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/harmony-gold-sees-modest-improvement-in-hidden-valley-output-for-quarter.html
Harmony Gold Mining Company Ltd.
said its Hidden Valley mine in  Papua New Guinea  faced
unscheduled mechanical downtime, according to a presentation to
analysts published on the company’s website today.  The company said Hidden Valley mine quarterly production
levels have “shown a positive trend” in the first half of the
year, however the third quarter is “likely to show only modest
improvement.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Agnes Nikoi at 
 anikoi@bloomberg.net  